>Mediator:(free)
  For minimal api 

>Mapster:(free)
  For mapping the object from one to another

>Razor lite , Fluid parser: (free)
  To render any model into text

>ITextsharp,aspos:(paid for commercial)
  To manage word and pdf

>LibreOffice:(free)
  convert word to pdf
  These are commandLine tools so we need a process to use these executable files.

>Ffmpeg:(free)
  To manage video files
  we can convert videos into segments for hls(http live streaming)
  This is a command line tool and we need a process to use this executable file

